						               													<description>These rules will enable you to play skirmish or adventure games, using 40mm or 28mm miniatures, from any era of history from the Prehistoric right through to the Napoleonic wars. Games can be played with as few as 2 figures and up to about 30 figures a side. Rules for stealth, fist fighting, martial arts. multiple combats, cavalry, spears and a whole host of other weapon types are included. Most games can be played in a couple of hours and so are suitable for club nights. Although these rules were primarily designed for our 40mm Samurai range, they could be used with our 28mm Prehistoric Settlement. These rules will also help you find a use for all those part finished armies that we all have. As you only need a small number of figures, taking up a new period need not be a vast and time consuming occupation.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game has a Character development section, enabling the Player to chart the progress of their Characters. So who knows maybe your peasant can make it and become a Warrior or even a Hero!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
